public enum PieceType
extends java.lang.Enum<PieceType>

The PieceType enum represents 8 different types of chess pieces: Pawn, Rook, Queen, King, Bishop, Knight, AntiKing, Empty, and Passant

The Passant piece is used when a Pawn can be attacked by an en passant. The Empty piece is used when there is no chess piece at a given location.
